  "clauseContent": "2.2.2.  免征、减征项目\n<div class=\"quill-better-table-wrapper\"><table class=\"quill-better-table\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><colgroup><col width=\"auto\"><col width=\"auto\"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-row=\"1\"><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">优惠类型</strong></p></td><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">具体项目</strong></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"2\"><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">免征企业所得税</span></p></td><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1.&nbsp;蔬菜、谷物、薯类、油料、豆类、棉花、麻类、糖料、水果、坚果的种植。</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2.&nbsp;农作物新品种的选育。</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.&nbsp;中药材的种植。</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">4.&nbsp;林木的培育和种植。</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">5.&nbsp;牲畜、家禽的饲养。</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">6.&nbsp;林产品的采集。</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">7.&nbsp;灌溉、农产品初加工、兽医、农技推广、农机作业和维修等农、林、牧、渔服务业项目。</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">8.&nbsp;远洋捕捞。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"3\"><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">减半征收企业所得税</span></p></td><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1.&nbsp;花卉、茶以及其他饮料作物和香料作物的种植。</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2.&nbsp;海水养殖、内陆养殖。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
